# =================================
# SECURITY NOTES
# =================================
# 1. Never commit real secrets to version control
# 2. Use different keys for each environment
# 3. Rotate MASTER_ENCRYPTION_KEY regularly
# 4. Set strong WEBHOOK_SECRET for signature verification
# 5. Use environment-specific S3 buckets
# 6. Enable database SSL in production (add ?sslmode=require to DATABASE_URL)